column1: #device_model_category : It corresponds to Type (Device Type) field of UI. Mandatory for Compute device and Meraki dashboard
#snmp_version, snmp_retries, snmp_timeout, protocol, cli_username, cli_password : Mandatory if device_model_category is NETWORK_DEVICE
#snmpv3_user_name, snmpv3_auth_type, snmpv3_auth_password, snmpv3_privacy_type, snmpv3_privacy_password : Mandatory if snmp_version is 3
#http_port, http_config_username, http_config_password, isdevicecompute, http_scheme  : Mandatory if device_model_category is COMPUTE_DEVICE
#if device_model_category is NETWORK_DEVICE or Empty, Required/Optional (columns with prefix - snmp and cli) and Not Required (columns with prefix - http)
#if device_model_category is COMPUTE_DEVICE or MERAKI_DASHBOARD, Required/Optional (columns with prefix - http) and Not Required (columns with prefix - snmp and cli)
#user needs to remove the commented lines (row 1 to 10) before importing
